cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CY 

This paper is about machine translation (MT) systems and their performance evaluation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves statistical analysis and the use of neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper focuses on comparing different MT paradigms, which could make it relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CY (Computational Geometry).
